	default strings That allows legacy clients connect.

2015-01-11  Nikos Mavrogiannopoulos <nmav@gnutls.org>

	* src/main.c, src/worker-misc.c, src/worker-vpn.c, src/worker.h: 
	simplified DTLS fd handling and dtls_pull()

